# ğŸ¤– AI-Powered Regulatory Compliance Checker for Contracts

This project automates the process of checking contracts against various regulatory standards such as **GDPR**, **DPA**, and **HIPAA** using Artificial Intelligence.
It extracts data from uploaded contract files, analyzes them, and flags compliance issues with detailed explanations.

