## ğŸŒŸ Features

- ğŸ“„ Extracts text and metadata from uploaded PDF contract files.
- ğŸ” Matches extracted content with predefined regulatory compliance templates.
- ğŸš© Detects and highlights non-compliant clauses.
- ğŸ“Š Generates a detailed report of compliance findings.
- ğŸ–¥ï¸ Provides a simple and interactive **Streamlit-based UI**.
- ğŸ”Œ Supports integration with multiple APIs for advanced NLP and legal text analysis.

